OL,6,FCommunities Minister Gordon Lyons has
OL,7,Fclaimed the body overseeing his
OL,8,Fdepartment "isn't a proper scrutiny
OL,9,Fcommittee" as MLAs clashed during a
OL,10,FStormont meeting.
OL,12,FIn heated exchanges on Thursday, Sinn
OL,13,FFein MLA and chairman of the
OL,14,FCommunities Committee, Colm Gildernew,
OL,15,Fsaid Mr Lyons had committed a "failure
OL,16,Fof leadership" and has tried to
OL,17,F"deflect and distract" criticism of
OL,18,Fhis performance.
