OL,6,FThe DUP minister has rejected the
OL,7,Freport, and his party leader Gavin
OL,8,FRobinson insisted the findings were
OL,9,F"totally irrational".
OL,11,FIn a fiery exchange on Thursday, Mr
OL,12,FGildernew opened his remarks to the
OL,13,Fminister by highlighting that the
OL,14,Fcommittee has previously taken a vote
OL,15,Fof no confidence in him.
OL,17,F"You minister have, it would appear,
OL,18,Fin Trumpian fashion, decided rather
OL,19,Fthan engage with the substance of that
OL,20,Freport you sought to deflect and
OL,21,Fdistract," he said.
