OL,6,F"What I would like to know, minister,
OL,7,Fis do you simply not care whether the
OL,8,Fpublic have confidence in you to
OL,9,Fdischarge your role?"
OL,11,FMr Lyons replied: "You've jumped in
OL,12,Fhere on this and this is your hour,
OL,13,Fyou have an hour with me and if you
OL,14,Fwant to go down that route I'm happy
OL,15,Fto, I have nothing to hide."
OL,17,FHe added: "We can go over this time
OL,18,Fand time again but I think that your
OL,19,Fstatement highlights yet again, just
OL,20,Fhow often you get it wrong.
